                    </p>
                    <a href="https://localhost:44302/Programmes#schedule" class="btn btnSuccess mt-3 mb-2 px-5 mx-auto">View Programmes</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row borderBrown-sm">
                <div class="col-sm-4 bgOrange p-2 "> <center><img class="img-fluid" src="~/Content/Images/Contact/site.png" /></center></div>
